\v 1 Kungani izikhathi\x + Tshu. 9.12. Isa. 13.22. Jer. 27.7. Hez. 22.3. 30.3.\x* zingafihlelwanga uSomandla\x + 15.20.\x*, labamaziyo bengaboni\x + 18.21.\x* insuku zakhe\x + 18.20. Isa. 13.6,9. Jow. 1.15. 2.1.\x*?
\v 2 Bathuthukisa imingcele\x + Dute. 19.14.\x*, baphange imihlambi bayeluse.
\v 3 Baxotsha ubabhemi wezintandane\x + Isa. 20.4.\x*, bathathe inkabi yomfelokazi ibe yisibambiso\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 4 Baphambula abaswelayo emigwaqweni\x + Amos 2.7. 5.12.\x*; abayanga bomhlaba\x + Hlab. 76.9. Zef. 2.3.\x* bacatsha ndawonye\x + 30.5,6. Zaga 28.28.\x*.
\v 5 Khangelani, bangobabhemi beganga enkangala\x + 6.5.\x*, baphumela emsebenzini wabo\x + Hlab. 104.23.\x*, badinge impango\x + Hlab. 104.21.\x* ngovivi\x + Hlab. 63.1.\x*; inkangala ibe yikudla kwakhe \add lo\add*kwabantwana.
\v 6 Emasimini bavuna ukudla kwakhe, bakhothoze \add e\add*sivini\add ni\add* somubi.
\v 7 Balala beze ebusuku bengelasembatho, bengelasigubuzelo emqandweni.
\v 8 Bamanzi ngezihlambo zezintaba\x + 8.16.\x*, babambelela edwaleni ngoba bengelasiphephelo\x + Lilo 4.5.\x*.
\v 9 Bahluthuna intandane ebeleni, bathathe lesibambiso kumyanga\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 10 Bahamba beze\x + 30.28. Hlab. 38.6. 104.26. 131.1. Lilo 5.18.\x* bengelasigqoko\x + 24.7. 31.19.\x*, labalambileyo bathwala isithungo\x + Jak. 5.4.\x*.
\v 11 Phakathi kwemiduli yabo bahluza amafutha\x + Jak. 5.4.\x*, banyathela izikhamelo zewayini, kodwa bomile\x + Hlu. 9.27. Isa. 63.2,3. Lilo 1.15.\x*.
\v 12 Abantu bayabubula besemzini\x + Hez. 30.24. Jer. 51.52.\x*, lomphefumulo wabalimeleyo uyakhala\x + Hez. 30.24. Jer. 51.52.\x*; kodwa uNkulunkulu ka\add ba\add*baleli ukungalungi\x + 1.22.\x*.
\v 13 Bona baphakathi kwabavukela ukukhanya; kabazazi indlela zakhe, kabahlali emikhondweni yakhe\x + Joha. 3.19,20.\x*.
\v 14 Umbulali uyavuka ngovivi, abulale umyanga loswelayo; lebusuku unjengesela.
\v 15 Lelihlo lesiphingi lilindela ukuhlwa, sisithi: Kakulalihlo elizangibona; sifake isimbombozo ebusweni baso.
\v 16 Emnyameni ugebha aphutshele ezindlini \add a\add*baziphawulele \add zona\add* emini; kabakwazi ukukhanya.
\v 17 Ngoba ikuseni kanyekanye ilithunzi lokufa kubo; uba besaziwa bakuzesabiso zethunzi lokufa.
\v 18 Ulula phezu kobuso bamanzi; isabelo sabo siqalekisiwe emhlabeni; kaphendukeli endleleni yezivini.
\v 19 Imbalela lokutshisa kuqeda amanzi eliqhwa elikhithikileyo, \add ngokunjalo\add* ingcwaba abonileyo.
\v 20 Isizalo sizamkhohlwa, impethu izammunya, engabe esakhunjulwa, lenkohlakalo izakwephulwa njengesihlahla.
\v 21 Udla ngokuminza inyumba engazaliyo, kamenzeli okuhle umfelokazi.
\v 22 Njalo udonsa abalamandla ngamandla akhe, uyavuka, njalo kungabi lolethemba lempilo\x + Hlab. 76.5.\x*.
\v 23 Uyamnika ukuze alondolozeke, eseyama kukho, kodwa amehlo akhe aphezu kwendlela zabo\x + 10.3. Hlab. 11.4.\x*.
\v 24 Bayaphakanyiswa okwesikhatshana, babesebengasekho, behliselwa phansi, bavalelwe njengaye wonke\x + Hlab. 37.10.\x*, bayaqunywa\x + 14.2.\x* njengesihloko sesikhwebu\x + Hlu. 12.6.\x*.
\v 25 Uba-ke kungenjalo, ngubani ongangenza umqambimanga, enze inkulumo yami ibe yize\x + 9.24.\x*?
